断矩阵</p><table-wrap id="table5" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table5">Table 5</xref></label><caption><title> B2-C Judgment matri</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" ></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >文化旅游收入C<sub>5</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >文化旅游人数C<sub>6</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >游客的重游率C<sub>7</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >游客人均消费C<sub>8</sub></th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >文化旅游收入C<sub>5</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >7</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >文化旅游人数C<sub>6</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/7</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/5</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >游客的重游率C<sub>7</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/3</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >游客人均消费C<sub>8</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表5. B<sub>2</sub>-C判断矩阵</p><table-wrap id="table6" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table6">Table 6</xref></label><caption><title> B3-C Judgment matri</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" ></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >旅游接待能力C<sub>9</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >交通设施完善程度C<sub>10</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >公共设施完善程度C<sub>11</sub></th><th align="center" valign="middle" >安全设施完善程度C<sub>12</sub></th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" 